.entry-header
About
Over 785 Acres of Peace and Relaxation
Escape to Sanlan RV & Golf Resort, where tranquility meets convenience. Nestled in nature yet close to Central Florida’s top attractions and the award-winning beaches of the Gulf Coast, our resort offers the perfect balance—whether you’re exploring Orlando and Tampa or simply unwinding in our natural sanctuary.
With shimmering lakes and over 7 miles of scenic trails, Sanlan provides a one-of-a-kind opportunity to observe Florida’s wildlife daily. From calming nature views to morning walks by the rookery—where herons, egrets, and even alligators thrive—you’ll discover countless ways to reconnect with the outdoors. The Sanlan Wildlife Sanctuary, right on property, adds to the wonder.
Spacious RV Sites
Spread across 785 acres, Sanlan offers more than 500 roomy RV sites designed for comfort and relaxation. Every site includes at no additional cost:
30-50 amp hook up service
Water
Electric
Sewer
Complimentary Wi-Fi
Complimentary 60 channel cable
Centraly accessible urban location makes us the perfect destination to participate in all that Central Florida has to offer yet our resort, with its many lakes and 7 miles of natural trails, provides an exclusive opportunity to observe Florida wildlife on a daily basis and enjoy the calming views of nature when you want to relax.
There’s no better way to start off the morning at Sanlan RV Park & Golf Resort than with a short hike to the rookery by the lake where you can observe water birds and alligators in the tree-lined waterways or enjoy the Sanlan Wildlife Sanctuary located on the grounds of the Sanlan RV Park.
Pet-Friendly RV Resort
We know your pets are family, which is why Sanlan is proud to be pet-friendly. Bring them along to share the trails, fresh air, and welcoming atmosphere that keep our guests returning year after year.
Dining and Shopping
Just minutes from the resort, you’ll find everything you need—grocery stores, restaurants, movie theaters, banks, and more. Whether you’re stocking up, dining out, or enjoying a night at the movies, convenience is never far away.
At Sanlan RV & Golf Resort, you’ll find more than just a place to stay—you’ll find an oasis of natural beauty, comfort, and relaxation. We look forward to welcoming you soon.
Learn more about all the great amenities Sanlan RV & Golf Resort has to offer.
